1. Setup Vundle via https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim
git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

2. Setup NerdTree via https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree
git clone https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree.git ~/.vim/bundle/nerdtree

3. Install Plugins
:PluginList
:PluginInstall
:PluginUpdate
